data.description: Hill Country Living at its best! This home on 10 ACRES has it all - awesome views and room to roam. This 1,984 sq. ft. modular home, built in 2015, has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, two living areas, and a huge kitchen. Enjoy your days swimming in the above ground pool, gardening, collecting eggs from the hen house, working on projects in the workshop or she-shed, or doing a bit of target practice. Watch the incredible sunsets from the huge front deck. By night, there's a stargazing deck and a firepit for roasting marshmallows. There's a nice yard fence for pets. Located about 20 mins. from Bandera, 15 mins. from Hondo, and 40 mins. from SA. Come and make this Medina County property your Hill Country home.
